{"status":0,"msg":"ok","result":{"channel":"头条","num":15,"list":[{"title":"伊利诺伊州已废除死刑 章莹颖案凶手会是死刑犯吗?","time":"2019-06-13 11:16:54","src":"封面新闻-华西都市报","category":"news","pic":"https:\/\/cms-bucket.ws.126.net\/2019\/06\/13\/3f883e05b3a041fea571e0f515e2d66d.png","content":"
